<div style="position:absolute;left:104.40px;top:550.14px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">→</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_008">駐車場の</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_008">入口は</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_008">どこか、わかりません。</span></div>
