<div style="position:absolute;left:159.60px;top:566.94px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">なん</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:201.60px;top:566.94px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">い</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:291.60px;top:566.94px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">おぼ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:570.54px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">1)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:104.40px;top:570.54px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">先生は  何と  言いましたか・覚えて  いません</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:414.60px;top:570.54px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">→</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:175.20px;top:587.34px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">え</span></div>
